qas.question: The Los Angeles Rams are an example of what kind of sports team?
The Los Angeles Clippers are a team belonging to which sport?
The Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim are from which sport?
What is the other NHL team aside from the Anaheim Ducks to reside in Southern California?
What is the lone MLS team that belongs to southern California?

plausible_answers.text: Los Angeles Rams, San Diego Chargers

qas.question: What NLF teams are from Southern California?

plausible_answers.text: Los Angeles Lakers, Los Angeles Clippers

qas.question: What NAB teams are from Southern California?

plausible_answers.text: Los Angeles Dodgers, Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim, San Diego Padres

qas.question: What MBL teams are from Southern California?
What NLH teams are from Southern California?
What MSL team is from Southern California?

context: Professional sports teams in Southern California include teams from the NFL (Los Angeles Rams, San Diego Chargers); NBA (Los Angeles Lakers, Los Angeles Clippers); MLB (Los Angeles Dodgers, Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim, San Diego Padres); NHL (Los Angeles Kings, Anaheim Ducks); and MLS (LA Galaxy).
